snippet.title: MLB 10 The Show (PS3) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
A full game of MLB 10 The Show, for PlayStation 3. Chicago White Sox at Minnesota Twins. 
 
Some highlights:
03:12 First pitch
31:08 Home run robbery
31:23 Somehow the color guy makes the home run robbery sound unimpressive?
42:00 First run scores
44:55 A defensive highlight that maybe looks a little silly in slow-mo
52:35 An RBI double
59:28 Ozzie Guillen is not happy
1:00:45 The big moment
1:05:08 The last pitch
